articles.title: Video captures police car crash that killed 65-year-old: authorities
articles.description: Video captured the moment a police cruiser crashed into a home in New Jersey, striking a 65-year-old woman who was walking outside, authorities said.
articles.content: The officer driving the vehicle, Garrell Middleton, was “responding to a radio alert of a crime in progress with the emergency lights on his patrol vehicle activated” at the time of the crash, the state’s attorney general’s office said in a statement...
